@NODE readmefirst "***** Read Me First *****"

This is a very early  BETA version of the Gadtools Source Code Creator for Blitz Basic
v2.1.  Its still in the early stages with lots of functions still to be added .(See
@{"To Do List" LINK "updates"})

All fucntions should work on thier own except for the requesters.  They require the
Reqtools.library to be copied to @{i}sys:Libs@{ui}. (Use installation script)

@ENDNODE

@NODE introduction "Introduction"

A while ago now when I was first learning blitz 2.1 I realised how tedious it was to
get the exact positions for the Gadgets in the windows.  So i thought 'wouldn't it be
great if you could use the mouse to create a GUI?'

I then started work on the very first version of this program for use for myself.
It was only designed to get the poistions for me and all tags and extras could be added
afterwards.

Not long afterwards I thought other people could benefit from this program so I
started work on adding extras to the program itself.  A next version was created for
release into the Public Domain as freeware.

@ENDNODE

