@NODE installation "Installation"

The program runs from anywhere as long as the directory contents are kept intact.

@ENDNODE

@NODE requirements "Requirements"

To run GT Code Creator you need:-

   * Gadtools.library
   * Reqtools.library
   * Blitz Basic v2.1
   * GTMenu shared library
   * Red Libs app library for the App functions

@ENDNODE

